shape: sequence_diagram

用户
Liaison
Pilot
VLM (Cognition)
Executor
工具 (MCP/gRPC)

用户 -> Liaison: 自然语言指令
Liaison -> Pilot: Intent
Pilot -> VLM (Cognition): 消息历史 + 工具列表

VLM (Cognition) -> Pilot: tool_calls {
  style.stroke: "#4285F4"
}
Pilot -> Executor: TaskGraph {
  style.stroke: "#4285F4"
}
Executor -> 工具 (MCP/gRPC): 工具调用 (按路由分发) {
  style.stroke: "#4285F4"
}
工具 (MCP/gRPC) -> Executor: 结果 {
  style.stroke-dash: 5
}
Executor -> Pilot: TaskCallEvent stream {
  style.stroke-dash: 5
}
Pilot -> VLM (Cognition): 追加结果，继续推理 {
  style.stroke: "#4285F4"
}

Pilot."(循环直到无 tool_calls)"

VLM (Cognition) -> Pilot: FinalText (循环终止) {
  style.stroke-dash: 5
}
Pilot -> Liaison: FinalText event {
  style.stroke-dash: 5
}
Liaison -> 用户: 结果 {
  style.stroke-dash: 5
}
